{"tid":775783,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"最on9既問題","createTime":"2018-08-11T12:30:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-11T12:53:53.000Z","uid":174652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ba91a067fdfea6003022e984507fb16a1e02ab8e","tid":775783,"uid":174652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:30:55.000Z","msg":"&quot;點解咁問&quot;, 呢句都係最冇腦既問題。<br />\n<br />\n當問人問題時, 如果對方覆返你&quot;點解咁問&quot;, 真係堅on9。而好多時你on99真係答左佢你點解咁問, 佢係唔會答你原先條問題。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c9ca011e4be96959cb90596f1a3432c9da946f","tid":775783,"uid":90820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:52:38.000Z","msg":"其實係想避而不答<br />\n所以先咁樣反問<br />\n之後就會扯開話題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"872996556e406d20060380b92cefb9d557e74ae2","tid":775783,"uid":134087,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-11T12:53:53.000Z","msg":"佢只係耍走你姐，你追問咪求其揾方法耍多你一次。<br />\n真係答問完都會答翻原本條問題"}]}